function ontab(s){$("#"+s+" span").bind({mouseover:function(){$("#"+s+" span").css({background:"#F5F5F5"}),$("#"+s+" span").css({borderBottom:"1px solid #D6D6D6"}),$("#"+s+" span").children("a").css({color:"#646464"}),$(this).css({background:"#FFF"}),$(this).css({borderBottom:"0"}),$(this).children("a").css({color:"#000"});var n=$("#"+s+" span").index(this);$("#"+s+" .content p").css({display:"none"}),$("#"+s+" .content p").eq(n).css({display:"block"})}})}ontab("tab1"),ontab("tab2");